        <p>Education Fundrasing can be used by an individual to raise funds for his <br>
           school or college fee. A fundraiser can also be started for a non-profit<br>
           organization aiming to educate the children from rural areas. Basically anyone <br>
           wanting to raise funds for education can choose crowdfunding.Fundraising<br>
           for education in India raises small amounts from a large group of <br>
           people online who are inspired by your determination and want you to succeed.<br> 
